snippet.title: Trailer Reveal | Amma: Chronicles of lost stars
snippet.description:
Amma: Chronicles of lost stars is developed by Joinplay Games, the new indie team of Noohkema interactive.

Amma: Chronicles of lost stars is a role-playing game set in an ancient civilization and where exploration, narration, and music will have a significant part. 
Music credit: Oumou Sangare - WMG; LatinAutor, BMI - Broadcast Music Inc.,  (We don't own the right)

Find out more about Amma: Chronicles of lost stars
Instagram: @joinplaygames
Twitter: @joinplaygames
Website: www.joinplaygames.com
